## 🔧 EXECUTION METHODOLOGY

### SOPv5.1 Cybernetic Execution Framework
- **Goal Analysis**: 100% test coverage with zero tolerance policy
- **Strategy Selection**: 16-agent maximum parallelization
- **Resource Allocation**: Container-only infrastructure with PHICS
- **Success Criteria**: All tests passing with comprehensive coverage

### TPS Integration
- **Jidoka**: Stop-and-fix at first test failure
- **5-Level RCA**: Systematic analysis of test failures
- **Continuous Improvement**: Pattern-based test enhancement
- **Respect for People**: Human oversight with AI coordination

### STAMP Safety Analysis  
- **STPA**: Proactive analysis of test failure scenarios
- **CAST**: Reactive analysis of critical test failures
- **Safety Constraints**: Zero test failures, 100% coverage
- **System Boundary**: Complete application stack testing

### TDG Methodology
- **Test-First**: All tests written before implementation
- **AI Code Generation**: Code generated to satisfy tests
- **Dual Property Testing**: PropCheck + ExUnitProperties
- **Coverage Validation**: 100% test coverage verification

